{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MediaSource.MediaSource()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/MediaSource","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Media_Source_Extensions_API\">Media Source Extensions API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource\"><code>MediaSource</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>MediaSource()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/activeSourceBuffers\"><code>activeSourceBuffers</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/duration\"><code>duration</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/sourceBuffers\"><code>sourceBuffers</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/addSourceBuffer\"><code>addSourceBuffer()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/clearLiveSeekableRange\"><code>clearLiveSeekableRange()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/endOfStream\"><code>endOfStream()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/isTypeSupported\"><code>isTypeSupported()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/removeSourceBuffer\"><code>removeSourceBuffer()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/setLiveSeekableRange\"><code>setLiveSeekableRange()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Media Source Extensions に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement/getVideoPlaybackQuality\"><code>HTMLVideoElement.getVideoPlaybackQuality()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBuffer\"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBufferList\"><code>SourceBufferList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>TextTrack.sourceBuffer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURL\"><code>URL.createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VideoPlaybackQuality\"><code>VideoPlaybackQuality</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VideoTrack/sourceBuffer\"><code>VideoTrack.sourceBuffer</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div></div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource\"><code>MediaSource</code></a> インターフェイスの <strong><code>MediaSource()</code></strong> コンストラクタは、ソースバッファが関連付けられていない新しい <code>MediaSource</code> オブジェクトを構築して返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>mediaSource</em> = new MediaSource();</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"パラメーター","isH3":true,"content":"<p>なし。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>次のスニペットは、Nick Desaulniers によって書かれた簡単な例から抜粋したものです（<a href=\"http://nickdesaulniers.github.io/netfix/demo/bufferAll.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ライブで完全なデモを見る</a>か、<a href=\"https://github.com/nickdesaulniers/netfix/blob/gh-pages/demo/bufferAll.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ソースをダウンロード</a>してさらに調査してください）。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> video <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'video'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> assetURL <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'frag_bunny.mp4'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Blink はコーデックに関して特定する必要がある</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ./mp4info frag_bunny.mp4 | grep Codec</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> mimeCodec <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'video/mp4; codecs=\"avc1.42E01E, mp4a.40.2\"'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'MediaSource'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> window <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> MediaSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isTypeSupported</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mimeCodec<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> mediaSource <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MediaSource</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//console.log(mediaSource.readyState); // closed</span>\n  video<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>src <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createObjectURL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mediaSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  mediaSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'sourceopen'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sourceOpen<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'サポートされていない MIME タイプまたはコーデック: '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> mimeCodec<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaSource.MediaSource","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/MediaSource/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBuffer\"><code>SourceBuffer</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/SourceBufferList\"><code>SourceBufferList</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"MediaSource インターフェイスの MediaSource() コンストラクタは、ソースバッファが関連付けられていない新しい MediaSource オブジェクトを構築して返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MediaSource()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MediaSource.MediaSource()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"MediaSource.MediaSource()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"MediaSource.MediaSource()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/mediasource/mediasource","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/mediasource/mediasource/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource","title":"MediaSource"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaSource/MediaSource","title":"MediaSource.MediaSource()"}],"pageTitle":"MediaSource.MediaSource() - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}